Farrah | فـــرّه
Farrah is a smart tourism website that showcases the natural beauty of Saudi Arabia. It features a rich collection of well-known and hidden natural destinations, each with detailed information including photos, key facts, weather updates refreshed every minute, an interactive map, and real visitor reviews.
One of Farrah’s standout features is its AI-powered itinerary generator, which asks users a few questions and then builds a fully personalized travel plan. This plan can even be downloaded and added directly to your phone’s calendar app.
The platform combines advanced features with a beautifully designed interface to deliver an immersive and enjoyable user experience.
